  "texts": [
    "In this space, closely related languages such as Czech and Slovak, or Urdu and Hindi, are close together, while unrelated and distant languages are far apart (S1 Fig).",
    "For thematic content type, there is no external space that could be easily plugged in, but it can be inferred directly from data.",
    "Many films in the Cinando database have more than one thematic tag.",
    "We infer the thematic space using the thematic tag co-occurrence information, analogously to how word vectors are inferred in Natural Language Processing (NLP).",
    "The rationale goes back to the notion of \"you shall know the word by the company it keeps\" [93]."
  ],
